  "notes": {
    "connections": "Keithley 0 (Power Supply)\n    CH1 \"3.3a\" \u2192 3.3 V, 1.5 A limit\n    CH2 \"3.3b\" \u2192 3.3 V, 1.5 A limit\n    CH3 \"P5V\" \u2192 5.0 V, 1.0 A limit\nHittite 0 RF_IN \u2192 SMA RF_IN (RF Band 3 input)\nHittite 1 LO    \u2192 SMA LO\nFieldFox 0 RF   \u2192 SMA IF output (IF Mode)",
    "sources": "Keithley 0 \u2013 DUT power: 3.3a @ 3.3 V, 3.3b @ 3.3 V, P5V @ 5.0 V\nHittite 0 \u2013 RF input drive @ 6 GHz, -25 dBm (within RF Band 3: 6-20 GHz)\nHittite 1 \u2013 LO drive @ 11 GHz, -5 dBm\nKeysight EL 0 \u2013 Electronic load (CH1 CC 0.1 A off, CH2 CR 10 k\u03a9 on)",
    "monitoring": "Keithley 0 \u2013 Monitor supply currents on 3.3a / 3.3b / P5V\nFieldFox 0 \u2013 IF output spectrum, center 6 GHz, span 10 GHz\n    (USB sideband: IF = LO - RF = 11 - 6 = 5 GHz)\nKeysight EL 0 \u2013 Monitor load currents / voltages",
    "general": "ADMV1420 Downconverter setup (per Memory Map / Side-By-Side view):\n    RF Band Select : RF Band 3 (6 GHz to 20 GHz)\n    IF Band Select : IF High Band (3 GHz to 13 GHz)\n    Output Select  : IF Mode (IF chain \u2192 DSA4/DSA5 \u2192 IF port)\n    Sideband       : LSB\n"
  }
